'''Ian Tapley''' co-wrote the backstory of [[Olana Chion/Legends|Olana Chion]], authored that of [[Antidar Williams/Legends|Antidar Williams']], and provided the first name for [[Tian Chyler]] in the [[Databank (original)|Databank]], through the ''[[What's The Story?]]'' feature of [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace]].

His alias was '''the fragrant wookiee''' on [[StarWars.com]].

